<div class="story"><p>Sea Scape is a golf course community on the west side of Rte 158 in Kitty Hawk. The homes and building lots are spread out around an 18 hole public golf course. The high elevation of the community offers horizon ocean views for the eastern most properties. Sea Scape has a mixture of second homes and primary residences and is located just past the condominium complex of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/sandpiper-cay.asp" title="Sandpiper Cay">Sandpiper Cay</a> and before you get to <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/southern-shores/" title="Southern Shores">Southern Shores</a> as you travel north on Rte 158. </p><p><a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/seascape-covenants-1.pdf" title="Seascape covenants section 1" target="_blank">Sea Scape Covenants Section 1</a> & <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/Sea-Scape-Covenants-Sec-2.pdf" title="Seascape covenants section 2" target="_blank">Sea Scape Covenants Section 2</a> & <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/sea-scape-covenants-3.pdf" title="Seascape covenants 3" target="_blank">Sea Scape Covenants 3</a>   - - - <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/Covenant-Disclaimer.asp" target="_blank"><b>    *</b></a></p>
